        "text": "為了我的名的緣故，我暫時不發怒； 為了我的名譽的緣故，我向你忍耐； 不把你剪除。"
      },
      "cunp": {
        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "我為我的名暫且忍怒， 為我的頌讚向你容忍， 不將你剪除。"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "For the sake of My name I delay My wrath, And for My praise I restrain it for you, In order not to cut you off."
      },
